These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-3-1::.
3 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, domino
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, filmmaking, board-games
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, martial-arts
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, may, april
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, cola
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, tennis, weightlifting
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 2. the person playing domino is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
 4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is the person playing domino##1
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching comedy movies##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 8. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |       3       |
| Game          | domino       | snooker   | scrabble      |
| Hobby           | board-games | woodworking      | filmmaking      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama        | comedy        | martial-arts  |
| Birthday   | april       | march     | may          |
| Beverage   | iced-tea      | fanta        | cola       |
| Sport         | tennis       | weightlifting | skateboarding |

