.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, february, june
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski, motorbike
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, collecting, reading
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, entrepreneur, videographer
House: art-deco, cottage, craftsman
3 different games are played: go, snooker, poker
 1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 2. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
 3. the cottage house is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the videographer and the analyst##2
 6. the entrepreneur is between the craftsman house and the person driving the motorbike##2
 7. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is the person playing poker##1
10. the videographer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |      3      |
| Birthday      | february        | june        | july |
| Transport          | motorbike       | jet-ski       | roller       |
| Hobby         | collecting   | reading      | baking      |
| Job           | videographer | entrepreneur | analyst     |
| House   | art-deco    | cottage        | craftsman        |
| Game           | poker        | go         | snooker        |

