The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, snowboarding, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is camping is the cain-smoker##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
3. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person traveling to colone##2
4. the modern house is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is the cain-smoker##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
7. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3       |
| City          | colone   | prague   | marseilles        |
| Hobby         | board-games | puzzles  | camping      |
| Cigar   | baccarat     | oliveros | cain       |
| House   | modern        | futuristic   | farmhouse       |
