The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, metal
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, egyptian, turkish
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, dannemann, game
 1. the egyptian is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
 2. the dannemann-smoker is the brazilian##1
 3. the owner of the pony is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 4. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
 7. the fan of metal is the siglo-smoker##1
 8. the fan of classical is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is basketball##2
 9. the turkish is between the person who growsrose and the person who growsamaryllis##2
10. the person who growsrose is on the right of the game-smoker##1
11. the brazilian is the dannemann-smoker##1
12. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |         3          |
| Pet      | pony     | turtle | goat              |
| Sport         | baseball   | badminton | basketball          |
| Flower           | amaryllis   | balloon-flower       | rose |
