3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, blend, bolivar
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, mauve, ivory
House: wooden, tower, colonial
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, volleyball
 1. the coach is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 2. the person who likes ivory is the person who likes ivory##1
 3. the coach is on the left or right of the designer##3
 4. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the wooden house##1
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is the colonial house##1
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the colonial house##1
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | cooking      | camping    | sudoku     |
| Job   | coach | designer    | firefighter |
| Cigar   | blend        | bluemaster | bolivar     |
| Color   | white       | ivory       | mauve   |
| House           | wooden   | colonial     | tower       |
| Sport         | baseball     | volleyball | parkour    |

