.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-3-19::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, azalea, amaryllis
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, vegafina, fonseca
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, r&b
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, ebony, emerald
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hedgehog, lizard
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, analyst, police-officer
1. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
2. the vegafina-smoker is the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
4. the police-officer is the fan of funk##1
5. the social-worker is between the person who likes emerald and the person who growsazalea##2
6. the police-officer is on the far right##1
7. the social-worker is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
8. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
9. the owner of the hedgehog is between the vegafina-smoker and the person who growsbellflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |
| Flower      | azalea   | amaryllis    | bellflower |
| Cigar   | vegafina     | bongani | fonseca     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | r&b         | funk        |
| Color   | ebony    | purple     | emerald    |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | hedgehog    | lizard      |
| Job         | analyst   | social-worker    | police-officer      |

