.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, british, nigerian
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, social-worker, software-developer
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, blood-red, black
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, bellflower, iris
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey, parkour
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, juice
1. the nigerian is the social-worker##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
4. the spanish is the person drinking sprite##1
5. the nigerian is the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the electrician is on the far left##1
7. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who growsiris is between the person who likes black and the person drinking sprite##2
9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |         2          |       3       |
| Nationality          | spanish     | british              | nigerian        |
| Job           | electrician | software-developer | social-worker |
| Color   | blood-red      | yellow             | black    |
| Flower   | orchid         | iris               | bellflower          |
| Sport         | badminton   | parkour            | ice-hockey    |
| Beverage     | sprite   | juice               | milk           |

 